Inside a Pod:
 â€¢ Each container runs a specific piece of the app (like a web server, logging agent, etc.)
 â€¢ They share the same IP address, hostname, and storage volumes
 â€¢ Pods are ephemeral â€” they can be terminated and recreated (not durable by default)

